        athought "She is rebuilding the model."

        athought "She is rebuilding it while I am still in the room. The rebuilding is in front of me but it is not for me. She is not showing me her work. She is doing her work in my presence."

        athought "The in-my-presence is what this hour was for."

        athought "She asked me to be a hand she could not predict. I was. She took the unpredictable input and now she is running the input into the new frame. The new frame is being built from the input."

        athought "I am one of the raw materials for the frame."

        athought "This is what it looks like when Noelle uses a person."

        athought "She said she wanted to be used functionally. She has been the one doing the using. I was the functional material."

        athought "I notice I am not resentful."

        athought "I am not resentful because the use was consensual in the most specific possible way. I was given the consent menu. I chose. The choice led to the use. The use produced the new frame she needed to build. The new frame is being built in front of me."

        athought "Being in the room while she builds the new frame is the thing I came here to receive without knowing I was coming to receive it."

        athought "I came here because a component of me reached for her in a way I could not name. The component received what it came for. The component is quiet now."

        athought "The commander-register is going to reassemble in approximately four minutes, when I walk back to the ops room. The commander-register is still functional. The commander-register was not removed by the hour. The hour was a separate room in the same building. The building is still the same building."

        athought "I am going to leave the alcove."

        athought "I am going to leave when she indicates the hour is complete."

        athought "The indication is going to be verbal or non-verbal. Either way I will receive it."

