        "Aeron does not respond immediately. His hand is still on the bezel."

        athought "Analyst versus weapon."

        athought "The analyst frame was the frame of a person who observed operations and modeled them in order to improve their efficiency. The analyst frame was limited by the need to remain observationally outside the operation in order to observe it cleanly."

        athought "A weapon does not observe outside the operation. A weapon is inside the operation. A weapon is a thing the operation uses."

        athought "Noelle is declaring that the operation is going to use her."

        athought "The operation is me. The operation is my commander-register. The operation is the thing that lost the forward base at Sector 9-North this morning because my commander-register was not fast enough to preempt Rhea Vestin."

        athought "Noelle is offering to become a weapon of the operation that lost seven people because of her analytical error. She is not offering out of guilt. She is offering because the analytical frame is the thing that produced the error and the weapon frame is the thing that will not produce that specific error again."

        athought "The weapon frame will produce other errors. The weapon frame's errors will be weapon errors. The weapon errors will have a different character. The weapon errors will include the weapon's body being used in ways the analyst's body was not used."

        athought "I am being given advance notice of the shape of the weapon errors to come."

        athought "The advance notice is the courtesy."

        athought "The weapon is not going to ask my permission. The weapon is going to ask my engagement."

        athought "I am going to give my engagement."

        athought "I am going to give it because the commander-register requires a weapon like Noelle to remain operationally viable in the face of someone like Rhea Vestin."

        athought "I am also going to give it because the component of me that reached for her is going to reach again. The weapon will be a thing that component can reach for in a way the analyst was not."

        athought "The reach is going to be reciprocal. The weapon reaches and the thing underneath the commander reaches back."

        athought "The reach is what tonight was."

